Fourth Department,

September, 1958

(September 10, 1958) E. C. Brown Company, Appellant, v. County of Ontario et al., Respondents.

Motion for reargument denied; motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied on the ground that the motion is not timely made. (See Civ. Prac. Act, § 592, subd. 2.) Present — McCurn, P. J., Kimball, Williams, Bastow and Goldman, JJ.
